HTML Attributes:| HTmL elements can have ettributes provide cdditional information about the elemements.
                | attributes are always specified in the start tag. attributes come in name/value pairs like height "10"
The Widht and Height Attributes:
The <img> tag sould also contain the width and height attributes which specifies the width and height of the image(in pixes)
                    <img src="UK.JPG" height="270" widht="540"


